{"tid":2496317,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"Sony：PS3及PSV網路商店將不會關閉","createTime":"2021-04-19T17:38:58.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-20T04:30:37.000Z","uid":105678,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"e7f06be012f66830ccb1920b6bfa9118b27e0ed3","tid":2496317,"uid":105678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T17:38:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmS4Ca5F7KKSzUbRjuuU9fTSMxunJvuZfGDdjtnkZmayNN?filename=gN9Znnz.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgN9Znnz.png&h=f3d66eac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n近期，我們曾通知玩家計劃於今年夏天結束PS3和PS Vita裝置上的PlayStation Store營運。<br />\n<br />\n然而，在進一步思考後，才發覺這決定顯然並不正確。因此今天很高興在這裡宣布，我們將保留PlayStation Store在PS3和PS Vita裝置上的營運。PSP商務功能則會按原訂計劃於2021年7月2日退役。<br />\n<br />\n最初決定要終止對PS3和PS Vita的購買支援，是考量到幾項因素，包括為舊裝置提供商務支援的挑戰性，以及可更集中資源在大多數玩家所操作的新裝置上。而現在我們看到了當中有許多人仍十分熱切能夠在可預見的未來繼續購買PS3和PS Vita上的經典遊戲，因此很開心我們能找出解決方案來繼續營運。<br />\n<br />\n很高興可以維持這傳承繼續供玩家享用，同時仍不斷地為PS4、PS5和次世代VR打造前衛的新遊戲世界。<br />\n<br />\n感謝大家所分享的回饋意見，我們始終聆聽並感激來自PlayStation社群的支持。"},{"pid":"b33f5a2a00077c4a6a0a7d15275cf40119800a60","tid":2496317,"uid":60164,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T17:43:15.000Z","msg":"佛心公司<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0fee0afc0ed566abbd94dcf08318ebe06ad733d8","tid":2496317,"uid":10056,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T17:46:43.000Z","msg":"真係想像唔到仲有人玩PS3 PSV同PSP<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca327b343ff411a7d00df51dae211f5e27ba015d","tid":2496317,"uid":634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T17:50:27.000Z","msg":"Jim Ryan良心發現？"},{"pid":"9fac19c85d162d323965bd8fb79100dadd825bf9","tid":2496317,"uid":263534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0fee0afc0ed566abbd94dcf08318ebe06ad733d8","tid":2496317,"uid":10056,"like":0,"